- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper involves natural language processing as it deals with speech signals. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a novel deep learning model for speech enhancement, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a new loss function for speech enhancement, which can be seen as a control problem.
